message: "If you use this framework, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "AI Citation Visibility Framework: MAHI Index, MAD-M Decay Model, and MAHI-100 Benchmark"
abstract: "A reproducible measurement framework for AI visibility across ChatGPT, Claude, Perplexity, Google AI Overviews, and Microsoft Copilot. Defines the MAHI Index (Marketing Agent Health Index), the MAD-M (Marketing Agent Decay Model), and the MAHI-100 benchmark protocol for evaluating how AI systems decide which businesses to cite. MAHI-100 is a public, reproducible 100-prompt benchmark protocol; it does not include completed benchmark results."
